DialogText: Y'know, Non Player Character. Like me, although the ones I'm refering to are just mindless idiots who walk around never uncrossing their hands. They're so stupid, that they sell things for EMERALDS! I know right? Anyways, we monitor them and let them roam around freely. Then, we send in some synthetic ones, "Synths" I like to call them. Identical in every way. I've seen NPCS like these however, that are much smarter. Check out Aquarius if you haven't already. Tons of them there. So I guess they're separated in 3 classes. Advanced, like me, Normal, like the ones that have somewhat developed minds, and Vegetables, like these. Fun to play around with huh?
